                <li class="col-lg-4">
                    <span class="fa-thumbnail fa-title" style="margin-top:0px;">
                        <a href="/en/ns/Living-with-dementia" id="twocolumn_0_leftcolumn_2_generalContentRepeater_ctl01_hrefImage" style="text-decoration:none;">
                            <img id="twocolumn_0_leftcolumn_2_generalContentRepeater_ctl01_imgModule" class="contentModuleImage" src="/ns/~/media/Images/national/Home%20page/AS-Homepage-CM4.jpg?h=137&amp;la=en&amp;w=224" alt="Living with dementia" style="border-width:0px;" />
                            
                            <span id="twocolumn_0_leftcolumn_2_generalContentRepeater_ctl01_litTitle" class="contentModuleText">Living with dementia</span>
                        </a>
                        <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>
                    </span>
                    <span class="fa-excerpt">
                        
                        <p>A diagnosis of dementia affects families and friends as well as the person with the disease. Learn how to help, support and reassure everyone who is living with dementia. </p>
<ul>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/Living-with-dementia/Day-to-day-living">Day to day living</a></li>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/Living-with-dementia/Staying-connected">Staying connected</a></li>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/Living-with-dementia/Planning-for-the-future">Planning for the future</a></li>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/About-dementia/Treatment-options">Treatment options </a></li>
</ul>
                    </span>
                </li>
                
            
                
                <li class="col-lg-4">
                    <span class="fa-thumbnail fa-title" style="margin-top:0px;">
                        <a href="/en/ns/We-can-help" id="twocolumn_0_leftcolumn_2_generalContentRepeater_ctl02_hrefImage" style="text-decoration:none;" title="We can help">
                            <img id="twocolumn_0_leftcolumn_2_generalContentRepeater_ctl02_imgModule" class="contentModuleImage" src="/ns/~/media/Images/national/Home%20page/AS-Homepage-CM2.jpg?h=137&amp;la=en&amp;w=224" alt="Getting help from the Alzheimer Society" style="border-width:0px;" />
                            
                            <span id="twocolumn_0_leftcolumn_2_generalContentRepeater_ctl02_litTitle" class="contentModuleText">We can help</span>
                        </a>
                        <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>
                    </span>
                    <span class="fa-excerpt">
                        
                        <p>Alzheimer Societies offer support, information and education in over 150 communities across Canada.</p>
<ul>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/We-can-help/Education">Education</a></li>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/We-can-help/Alzheimer-InfoLine">Alzheimer InfoLine<br />
    </a></li>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/We-can-help/Resources">Resources</a></li>
    <li><a href="http://www.safelyhome.ca" target="_blank">Safely Home<sup>&reg;</sup></a><sup></sup> </li>
</ul>
                    </span>
                </li>
                
            
                </ul><ul class="fa-items row">
                <li class="col-lg-4">
                    <span class="fa-thumbnail fa-title" style="margin-top:0px;">
                        <a href="/en/ns/Get-involved" id="twocolumn_0_leftcolumn_2_generalContentRepeater_ctl03_hrefImage" style="text-decoration:none;" title="Get involved">
                            <img id="twocolumn_0_leftcolumn_2_generalContentRepeater_ctl03_imgModule" class="contentModuleImage" src="/ns/~/media/Images/national/Home%20page/AS-Homepage-CM3.jpg?h=137&amp;la=en&amp;w=224" alt="Women showing a young boy how to play the violin. " style="border-width:0px;" />
                            
                            <span id="twocolumn_0_leftcolumn_2_generalContentRepeater_ctl03_litTitle" class="contentModuleText">Get involved</span>
                        </a>
                        <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>
                    </span>
                    <span class="fa-excerpt">
                        
                        <p>You can help! Find out all the ways you can get involved in your own way in your own time.</p>
<ul>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/Get-involved/Volunteer">Volunteer</a></li>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/Get-involved/Raise-your-voice">Raise your voice</a></li>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/Get-involved/Be-a-fundraiser">Be a fundraiser</a></li>
</ul>
                    </span>
                </li>
                
            
                
                <li class="col-lg-4">
                    <span class="fa-thumbnail fa-title" style="margin-top:0px;">
                        <a href="/en/ns/Research" id="twocolumn_0_leftcolumn_2_generalContentRepeater_ctl04_hrefImage" style="text-decoration:none;">
                            <img id="twocolumn_0_leftcolumn_2_generalContentRepeater_ctl04_imgModule" class="contentModuleImage" src="/ns/~/media/Images/ns/Content%20modules/MBTB%201__researchmodule.jpg?h=137&amp;la=en&amp;w=224" style="border-width:0px;" />
                            
                            <span id="twocolumn_0_leftcolumn_2_generalContentRepeater_ctl04_litTitle" class="contentModuleText">Research</span>
                        </a>
                        <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>
                    </span>
                    <span class="fa-excerpt">
                        
                        <p>The Alzheimer Society offers hope for tomorrow by funding research to find a cure and support quality of life for people living with dementia.</p>
<ul>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/Research/Alzheimer-Society-Research-Program">Alzheimer Society Research Program</a></li>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/Research/Alzheimer-s-disease-research">Alzheimer's disease research</a></li>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/Research/Research-in-Nova-Scotia">Research in Nova Scotia</a> </li>
    <li><a href="/en/ns/Research/Research-in-Nova-Scotia/Information-for-researchers">Participating in research </a></li>
</ul>
                    </span>
                </li>
                
            
    </ul>
</div>

	</section>
